objects.name: Dino_Player
objects.string:
Now listen carefully. 
You have been asleep for a long time. 
Those little creatures stole your eggs!
You need to collect them all to be able to escape. 
You need to keep your eggs close and warm to be a good mother. 
You cannot leave a single egg behind you must find them all to move on.
